msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/articles/software-raid-p1.xml:443
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Yay! Our RAID device is up and running. All we need to do now \n"
"is create a filesystem on it. To do this, use the \n"
"<c>mke2fs</c> command or the <c>mkreiserfs</c> command \n"
"(RAID-0 and ReiserFS is a great combination!):\n"
msgstr ""

